trans-unit.source: Specifies a new or an existing location that you want to use for production operations.

trans-unit.source: Specifies an existing VAT product group that will be used for items.

Page Create Contoso Demo Data - Control Base VAT Code - Property Caption

trans-unit.source: Specifies existing business posting groups and, if relevant, VAT posting groups that will be applied to the vendors that will be added. The Domestic group is a great choice.
trans-unit.target: Spécifie les groupes comptabilisation marché existants et, le cas échéant, les groupes comptabilisation TVA qui seront appliqués aux fournisseurs qui seront ajoutés. Le groupe National est un excellent choix.

Page Create Contoso Demo Data - Control Domestic Code - Property Caption

trans-unit.source: Specifies a new inventory posting group that will be used for finished items.

Page Create Contoso Demo Data - Control Finished Code - Property Caption

trans-unit.source: Specifies a new product group that will be used to map capacity transactions.
trans-unit.target: Spécifie un nouveau groupe produits qui sera utilisé pour mapper les transactions de capacité.
trans-unit.note: Page Create Contoso Demo Data - Control Manufact Code - Property ToolTip

trans-unit.source: Specifies new product and inventory posting groups that will be used for raw materials items.

trans-unit.source: Specifies an existing product posting group that will be used for finished items. The Retail group is a great choice.

trans-unit.source: Specifies a factor to convert a price from USD/EUR to your local currency. 1 means that the price is 149 in any currency. A higher number will be used to get the price in your local currency.
